reviewText: Very well done and I was in a jet fighter squadron a few years ago.
I would rank this number 2 in the "Legends of Air Combat" series, behind the "B-52" one.  It is largely an enjoyable program
I'd recommend this DVD to military fans. The narraration leaves something to be desired, but the film footage is great. I do wish they spent more time on the F-15s time to climb records.

A fairly basic documentary, For someone new to military jets this is a good video for them, but to
those jet enthusiasts looking for more than the basics,forget it. The footage is somewhat grainy and dated therefore it gets a 3 star rating.
